                <mxCell id="corr-explain" value="The Correlation ID is essential for matching requests with responses:&#xa;&#xa;• Client generates unique ID (UUID) for each request&#xa;• ID included in request message header&#xa;• Server copies ID to response message&#xa;• Client uses ID to match response to original request&#xa;• Enables multiple concurrent requests" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;spacingLeft=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
